a. 
Source of stimulus: the owner of Cinema
Stimulus: enhance Security system for purchase ticket using Credit Cards by detecting false information in credit card
Environment: System
Artifact: under normal operations
Response: ticketing system stops processing process and directs to error message when user entered false credit card information 
Response measure: system successfully detect errors 100% under 5 seconds

b.
Source of stimulus: the owner of Cinema
Stimulus: increase the performance of booking tickets 
Environment: System
Artifact: under normal operations
Response: process transaction of booking tickets 
Response measure: with average latency of 2 seconds and process 1000 transactions per second
